{
  "chunks": [
    {
      "chunk_id": "e48718aae509",
      "text": "# 商品保养指南",
      "source_file": "care_guide.md",
      "metadata": {
        "filepath": "/Users/yy/langgraph-agent-harness-v4/knowledge/raw/care_guide.md",
        "start_char": 0
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "6b591ce8f158",
      "text": "## 防晒衣清洗\nUPF50+ 轻薄防晒衣建议冷水手洗，使用中性洗涤剂，不可漂白，不可高温烘干。洗后自然晾干即可，不要暴晒。",
      "source_file": "care_guide.md",
      "metadata": {
        "filepath": "/Users/yy/langgraph-agent-harness-v4/knowledge/raw/care_guide.md",
        "start_char": 10
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "35224c0cf77c",
      "text": "## 运动外套保养\n轻量运动外套建议冷水轻柔机洗，使用洗衣袋，不可漂白。防泼水涂层会随洗涤次数逐渐减弱，建议减少洗涤频率。",
      "source_file": "care_guide.md",
      "metadata": {
        "filepath": "/Users/yy/langgraph-agent-harness-v4/knowledge/raw/care_guide.md",
        "start_char": 74
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "7b12933b0d63",
      "text": "## 遮阳帽清洗\n可折叠遮阳帽手洗或轻柔机洗均可，自然晾干即可。帽檐部分不要用力折叠，以免变形。",
      "source_file": "care_guide.md",
      "metadata": {
        "filepath": "/Users/yy/langgraph-agent-harness-v4/knowledge/raw/care_guide.md",
        "start_char": 137
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "4d899677941e",
      "text": "## 不同材质注意事项\n- 锦纶混纺面料：耐穿易干，但避免高温熨烫\n- 聚酯纤维面料：快干耐洗，但不可高温烘干\n- 速干面料：适合户外使用，建议冷水洗",
      "source_file": "care_guide.md",
      "metadata": {
        "filepath": "/Users/yy/langgraph-agent-harness-v4/knowledge/raw/care_guide.md",
        "start_char": 187
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "a5797c07565a",
      "text": "## 存放建议\n换季收纳时应保持干燥，避免潮湿环境。防晒衣和运动外套建议悬挂存放，遮阳帽可折叠收纳。",
      "source_file": "care_guide.md",
      "metadata": {
        "filepath": "/Users/yy/langgraph-agent-harness-v4/knowledge/raw/care_guide.md",
        "start_char": 264
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "a784fcc47823",
      "text": "# 常见问题",
      "source_file": "faq_long.md",
      "metadata": {
        "filepath": "/Users/yy/langgraph-agent-harness-v4/knowledge/raw/faq_long.md",
        "start_char": 0
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "3a63f6ef9dda",
      "text": "## 发货时效\n现货商品一般在 48 小时内发货，预售商品以页面标注的发货时间为准。发货后会通过短信通知物流单号。",
      "source_file": "faq_long.md",
      "metadata": {
        "filepath": "/Users/yy/langgraph-agent-harness-v4/knowledge/raw/faq_long.md",
        "start_char": 8
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "648d8ef40232",
      "text": "## 物流查询\n快递发出后通常在 3-5 个工作日内到达，具体时效因地区而异。您可以在订单页面查看物流信息，或联系客服提供订单号查询。",
      "source_file": "faq_long.md",
      "metadata": {
        "filepath": "/Users/yy/langgraph-agent-harness-v4/knowledge/raw/faq_long.md",
        "start_char": 67
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "5dfa31638f83",
      "text": "## 尺码选择建议\n建议根据商品详情页的尺码表选择。如果拿不准，可以测量平时穿着的衣服尺寸对比尺码表，或提供身高体重咨询客服。",
      "source_file": "faq_long.md",
      "metadata": {
        "filepath": "/Users/yy/langgraph-agent-harness-v4/knowledge/raw/faq_long.md",
        "start_char": 136
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "911a128ce1f5",
      "text": "## 售后联系\n客服服务时间为每天 9:00-21:00。您可以通过在线客服、客服电话或留言方式联系我们。售后问题请提供订单号和问题描述。",
      "source_file": "faq_long.md",
      "metadata": {
        "filepath": "/Users/yy/langgraph-agent-harness-v4/knowledge/raw/faq_long.md",
        "start_char": 201
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "7e91f7ef2aac",
      "text": "## 推荐场景\n- 夏季通勤推荐防晒衣，轻薄透气且有 UPF50+ 防晒指数\n- 运动健身推荐轻量外套，防风防泼水且弹性好\n- 户外旅行推荐遮阳帽，可折叠便携且防晒",
      "source_file": "faq_long.md",
      "metadata": {
        "filepath": "/Users/yy/langgraph-agent-harness-v4/knowledge/raw/faq_long.md",
        "start_char": 272
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "a0c54ecc31ce",
      "text": "## 价格说明\n商品价格以页面标价为准，价格可能因活动有所浮动。促销活动期间价格可能会有调整。",
      "source_file": "faq_long.md",
      "metadata": {
        "filepath": "/Users/yy/langgraph-agent-harness-v4/knowledge/raw/faq_long.md",
        "start_char": 356
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "b0a2b9aa0171",
      "text": "# 退换货政策",
      "source_file": "refund_policy.md",
      "metadata": {
        "filepath": "/Users/yy/langgraph-agent-harness-v4/knowledge/raw/refund_policy.md",
        "start_char": 0
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "71b1f6218a01",
      "text": "## 7 天无理由退换货\n商品不影响二次销售的情况下，签收后 7 天内可申请无理由退换货。退货运费由买家承担（商品质量问题除外）。",
      "source_file": "refund_policy.md",
      "metadata": {
        "filepath": "/Users/yy/langgraph-agent-harness-v4/knowledge/raw/refund_policy.md",
        "start_char": 9
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "d488190ea5a7",
      "text": "## 质量问题处理\n如果商品存在质量问题（破损、染色、尺码严重不符等），请在签收后 48 小时内联系客服，提供照片或视频凭证。核实后我们将承担退货运费并为您办理退换货或退款。",
      "source_file": "refund_policy.md",
      "metadata": {
        "filepath": "/Users/yy/langgraph-agent-harness-v4/knowledge/raw/refund_policy.md",
        "start_char": 76
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "c9d27356565f",
      "text": "## 非质量问题退换限制\n以下情况不支持无理由退换：\n- 已水洗或穿着过的商品\n- 吊牌已拆除的商品\n- 贴身衣物（内裤、袜子等）\n- 超过 7 天签收的商品",
      "source_file": "refund_policy.md",
      "metadata": {
        "filepath": "/Users/yy/langgraph-agent-harness-v4/knowledge/raw/refund_policy.md",
        "start_char": 165
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "8f6073b0422c",
      "text": "## 二次退款说明\n如果用户第二次明确要求退款，系统会进入退款流程。退款金额将原路返回，预计 3-5 个工作日到账。",
      "source_file": "refund_policy.md",
      "metadata": {
        "filepath": "/Users/yy/langgraph-agent-harness-v4/knowledge/raw/refund_policy.md",
        "start_char": 246
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "be069f79ff78",
      "text": "## 多次退款说明\n如果用户多次申请退款（三次及以上），系统会触发人工审核，由人工客服确认后处理。",
      "source_file": "refund_policy.md",
      "metadata": {
        "filepath": "/Users/yy/langgraph-agent-harness-v4/knowledge/raw/refund_policy.md",
        "start_char": 306
      }
    },
    {
      "chunk_id": "79a4c905cc9b",
      "text": "## 需要人工确认的情况\n以下情况需要转人工客服处理：\n- 情绪评分超过 0.85\n- 用户明确要求人工\n- 投诉类问题\n- 系统错误\n- 多次退款请求",
      "source_file": "refund_policy.md",
      "metadata": {
        "filepath": "/Users/yy/langgraph-agent-harness-v4/knowledge/raw/refund_policy.md",
        "start_char": 357
      }
    }
  ],
